      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention, including engine repairs and a suspension overhaul, and is not recommended for immediate daily driving. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches, faded paint, and several dents, while the interior has substantial tearing and staining. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or a source for spare parts.",
